ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
SubjectOrder Transferring from the Department of Industry to the Federal Economic Development Agency for Southern Ontario the Control an Supervision of the Southern Ontario Regional Economic Development Branch
PrecisOrder transferring the control and supervision of the portion of the federal public administration known as the SOUTHERN ONTARIO REGIONAL ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT BRANCH from the Department of Industry to the Federal Economic Development Agency for Southern Ontario, effective August 13, 2009.
